  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large fondue pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the orange zest and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the lemon juice, orange juice, and honey, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes, until thickened slightly.",
    "Stir in the flour and cook for 1 minute, until smooth.",
    "Add the almonds and pistachios and stir to combine.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped parsley.",
    "Cook time will vary depending on the size of the fondue pot."
